node.text:
First time in Boeing 737-800 Sim! Although I am Airbus Fan, it was a great experience flying B737! It’s great to feel the yoke flying Again! Thank you, @nationalflightcentre, for the great tour, hospitality and for giving me the chance to fly different simulators, including B737! 
Also, I Had the pleasure to meet many brilliant students, including @kevin0reilly , and listening to his story about how he changed his whole career to pursue his dream of becoming a pilot 👨‍✈️! 
It’s great to see the resilience of students and ATOs during these challenging times! 
Great stories, great motivation, and more determination to achieve goals and dreams!
A320 or B737? What’s your Favorite 😍 
.
.
.
.
.
